Question:
Set up password-less SSH authentication between jump host and app servers.

Answer:

Generated SSH key pair:

ssh-keygen -t rsa


Copied public key to app servers:

ssh-copy-id -i ~/.ssh/id_rsa.pub tony@stapp01


Verified login:

ssh tony@stapp01


âœ… Achieved password-less login successfully.
